Package uk.org.ury.backend.server.exceptions

Exception Summary
BadRequestException Exception thrown when the server meets a malformed request, or part of one.
HandleFailureException Generic exception thrown when a server request handler fails to handle a request.
HandlerNotFoundException Exception thrown when the server request handler requested by the client is not * found in the class space.
HandlerSetupFailureException Exception thrown when the server request handler requested by the client cannot be set up to process the request.
HandlingException Generic exception thrown when the server cannot handle a request.
NotAHandlerException Exception thrown if the class requested as a handler by the client is, in fact, not a handler (it does not implement RequestHandler).
UnknownFunctionException Exception thrown when a handler receives a request for a path that does not correspond to one of its functions.
